OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,FThe owner of Sea Life London Aquarium
OL,8,Fhas promised to phase out gentoo
OL,9,Fpenguins at all of its UK facilities,
OL,10,Fmarking a win for wildlife campaigners.
OL,12,FMerlin Entertainments said in a
OL,13,Fstatement that it would merge the 14
OL,14,Fpenguins in the London site with the
OL,15,F17 housed at their Birmingham facility
OL,16,Finto a single colony with a new
OL,17,Fhabitat that has natural light and
OL,18,Fmore water space.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
