FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,FThe multinational firm also committed
OL,8,Fto ending breeding of the birds
OL,9,Fpermanently after holding two-days of
OL,10,Ftalks over the issue last week.
OL,12,FIt comes after campaigners have long
OL,13,Fcalled on bosses to provide better
OL,14,Fconditions for the penguins, who are
OL,15,Fhoused in an indoor basement enclosure
OL,16,Fin London without access to fresh air
OL,17,For daylight.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,FFreedom for Animals, the Born Free
OL,8,FFoundation, the Daily Express
OL,9,FNewspaper, MPs and members of the
OL,10,Fpublic all joined the campaign, with
OL,11,Fsome urging the firm to move the
OL,12,Fpenguins outdoors.
OL,14,FThe company, which is one of the
OL,15,Flargest aquarium operators in the
OL,16,Fworld, said it will confirm a full
OL,17,Fproposal for the improved enclosure by
OL,18,FSeptember, adding it will likely be
OL,19,Fbased at the London Aquarium.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,FFreedom for Animals and Born Free will
OL,8,Fbe consulted on its design before a
OL,9,Ffinal decision is made, it added.
OL,11,FA Merlin Entertainments spokeswoman
OL,12,Fsaid the firm "intends to merge its
OL,13,Ftwo UK gentoo colonies into a single,
OL,14,Fenhanced home, with significantly
OL,15,Fenlarged water space, and natural
OL,16,Flight; and permanently end gentoo
OL,17,Fbreeding at both London and Birmingham
OL,18,Fsites".
OL,26,@tD@OOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
