OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,FIt followed months of collaboration
OL,8,Fwith Freedom for Animals, the Born
OL,9,FFree Foundation and People for the
OL,10,FEthical Treatment of Animals (Peta), a
OL,11,Fwild penguin researcher, a
OL,12,Fveterinarian, and the British and
OL,13,FIrish Association of Zoos and
OL,14,FAquariums (Biaza), it said.
OL,16,FThe firm recognised some stakeholders
OL,17,Fwish to keep open the prospect of
OL,18,Fmoving the gentoo penguins to an
OL,19,Foutdoor facility, or a newly created
OL,20,Fsanctuary because none currently exist
OL,21,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,F"While there are a small number of
OL,8,Fpotentially suitable outside locations
OL,9,Fin the UK, any move beyond Merlin
OL,10,Fsites removes our ability to honour
OL,11,Fthe commitment we have made to stop
OL,12,Fbreeding permanently," they said.
OL,14,F"Knowing the significant complexities
OL,15,Fand resources required to sustain a
OL,16,Fsanctuary offering excellent welfare
OL,17,Facross the lifespan of the animals, we
OL,18,Fdo not believe this is a realistic
OL,19,Foption for these penguins.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@VO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,F"With both of these factors in mind,
OL,8,Fthe group focused on developing a
OL,9,Fclear, science-led path to continue to
OL,10,Fenhance the habitat for the gentoos in
OL,11,FMerlin's care, while contributing to
OL,12,Ffurther conservation research and
OL,13,Fvisitor education for this species.
OL,15,F"We care deeply about these penguins
OL,16,Fand have always been focused on
OL,17,Fproviding them with the best possible
OL,18,Flife, now and in the future.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
