PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780063874
OL,3,CLondon Aquarium owner commits to
OL,4,Cending gentoo penguin exhibits across
OL,5,CUK venues
OL,7,F"This decision was reached following a
OL,8,Frobust consultative process, with
OL,9,Fsignificant input from experts.
OL,11,F"We are grateful for the energy,
OL,12,Fexpertise and time everyone has
OL,13,Finvested."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@JO]
